title: Dash Go Salad Chef
description: The Dash Go Salad Chef is a slim, compact, and versatile slicer and shredder that makes quick work of cucumbers, carrots, and even hard vegetables like beets. The five cone attachments--thick slicer, thin slicer, fine shredder, coarse shredder, and grater--are easy to pop onto the machine, and store neatly in the conveniently built-in storage compartment.
